{
  "stem": "2590.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll tell the dog-- I'll-- the dog is going to-- to-- to pull you apart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, whatever I had, I threw out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he called off the dog.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came to Nadia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I begged her, I said, what can you do for me?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was already 1943-- almost the end of 1943.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only did we have enemies, the Germans, the Ukrainians were our own enemies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Poles were our enemies-- very, very few people that were really sympathetic to our cause-- very few.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the reason so few of us survived, like it would happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Germans came to Holland or they came to Denmark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people-- the Danish people-- put on the Jewish stars too And they sympathized, but with us, the Poles, they gave us up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us to the German authority.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this Nadia Honovska told me there was this village, a Polish village, where a certain sect of Ukrainians-- they were called [NON-ENGLISH]-- and they hated the Poles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they killed out the whole population.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very small village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the people, they used to do such horrid things-- to cut off men's penises, or women's breasts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And nobody remained alive except for a few people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that Nadia told me the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, and the people, the few people that remained alive from that village, [NON-ENGLISH] that village-- they went to work-- to look for work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had Czechish colonies in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she suggested I should do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She brought me a little cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I was at her attic, and sometimes when I came into the house to-- to cook, I had an opportunity to study prayers, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
